{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act9d0_level_act9d0_05_end","storyGroup":"act9d0","storySort":10,"storyDependence":"act9d0_level_act9d0_05_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DM-7","storyName":"龟裂","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"为了将自己的见闻告知W，伊内丝铤而走险，并遭遇了整合运动的拦截，最后的时刻，她的眼前唯有阴影。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act9d0/level_act9d0_05_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act9d0_07","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":8,"next":10,"characters":["赫德雷","伊内丝","整合运动士兵","坚毅的整合运动术师"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Character","id":4},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Dialog","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"Text","text":"塔露拉变了。","id":8},{"type":"Text","text":"第一次见到塔露拉的时候，她给我的感觉，和特蕾西娅殿下很像。","id":9},{"type":"Text","text":"但殿下一直非常的悲伤，她背负着......也知晓着这片大地的更多秘密。","id":10},{"type":"Text","text":"塔露拉不同，她很愤怒，足够冷静的，却又充满热情的愤怒。","id":11},{"type":"Text","text":"虽然细小很多，却同样强盛。也许他们这样的人无论力量大小，都拥有着近似的部分。","id":12},{"type":"Text","text":"这股愤怒催生了整合运动，让无数追随者趋之若鹜。","id":13},{"type":"Text","text":"但很快......就改变了。","id":14},{"type":"Text","text":"我们每天的工作，变成了煽动、加害和挑拨。","id":15},{"type":"Text","text":"这不再是一场感染者的革命——","id":16},{"type":"Text","text":"——而是我们在卡兹戴尔目睹过无数次的，被过度操纵的战争阴谋。","id":17},{"type":"Dialog","id":18},{"type":"Character","id":19},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_cher_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":21},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_047","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"她没有追上来。","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......如果我们真的和她正面碰上，事情就麻烦了。","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你不该对塔露拉使用法术，这也不是第一次了，我们要时常小心自己看见的东西。","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......塔露拉的身上一定发生了什么，这件事必须告诉W。","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"多亏了W几次的小动作，我们已经遭到那些暴徒的猜忌了，这还不够吗？","id":31,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你到底看到了什么？","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"过去的塔露拉只是个反抗者。她把反抗的机会带给那些被解放的感染者。","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"现在呢？他们几乎毫不收敛自己的欲望，单纯的破坏，滥杀。","id":35,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"这不足以说明什么，萨卡兹之外的种族对感染者素来如此。","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......你不明白。","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我不是在说这种行为本身怎么了，我是在说这样的行为会招致什么后果......","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"塔露拉她......在葬送整合运动，刻意的。","id":41,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......为什么？","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"你不觉得这个情况似曾相识吗？","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"她是个优秀的领袖，能将这些普通的感染者卷入战争，甚至带给他们胜利。","id":46,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"但她，也只有她才能用最神不知鬼不觉的方法，一步步毁掉自己一手搭建起来的高塔。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"甚至......","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"甚至塔露拉她自己，都只是其中一块比较精美的砖瓦，随时可以被粉碎。","id":49,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你是在说......","id":51,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"和三年前给我的感觉一样。","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"但他......他或许素来如此，他可以毫不犹豫地做到这一切......只是藏的很好罢了。","id":54,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"塔露拉不同，她的变化太突然了。","id":55,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"她的影子......她甚至有两个影子，不像是法术的痕迹，倒像是......","id":56,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"一座废墟，古老，强盛，满是那种力量的残留......","id":57,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你的法术性质很特殊，尽管如此，你这次的感觉也太模糊了，这还是不构成行动的理由。","id":59,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"但这件事W必须知道！","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"小声点，我们已经被注意到了。","id":63,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"任何动作都会成为别人的把柄，你明白的。","id":64,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"那你觉得我们还能经受住第二次巴别塔那样的变故吗？","id":66,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我不确定......","id":68,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......至少W不能。","id":70,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"我去找她，既然加尔森已经死了，她就是新的领导人。","id":71,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"2","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"等等！如果塔露拉真的已经注意到了，你这样会——","id":73,"figure":"avg_npc_047"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","name2":"avg_npc_047","focus":"1","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"等不了，别想命令我，现在我们还是平起平坐。","id":75,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......哼。","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"话是这么说，这好像是我第一次抗命。","id":77,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"你不该总是想这么多的，赫德雷。","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":79},{"type":"Dialog","id":80},{"type":"Character","id":81},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_cher_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":83},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":84},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","crossfade":"5","volume":"0.4","id":85,"musicid":1},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","id":86},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"（W，就在前面，穿过这条巷子就......）","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"（那里不是营地？她在做什么？）","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"（总之得快一点——）","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"——","id":92,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"——谁？","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"......","id":95,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"感染者......？有什么事吗？","id":97,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"注意你的语气，魔族。","id":99,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"先是有几支佣兵队伍叛逃，接着又让敌人出现在了城内。","id":100,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"你们犯下的错误太多，你该不会以为领袖没有看在眼里吧？","id":101,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"让开，我没有义务听你抱怨。","id":103,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"你有这个义务对塔露拉负责。","id":105,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"——我明白了，等我向W汇报完之后，我会去向塔露拉报到。","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"不必了。","id":109,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"我们需要的不是这种“负责”。","id":110,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"什么......","id":112,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialog","id":113},{"type":"Character","id":114},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":116},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":117},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":119},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_052","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"啧.....来真的？","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_052"},{"type":"Dialog","id":122},{"type":"Character","id":123},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":124},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":125},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":126},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":127},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":128},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":130},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":132},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":133},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"刚才发生的袭击波及了这里，萨卡兹雇佣兵小队长之一的伊内丝，死亡。","id":135,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"2","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"坚毅的整合运动术师","text":"不去确认她的尸体？","id":137,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"......刚才的战斗动静太大，已经有人被吸引过来了，立刻炸毁这条街道。","id":139,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"2","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"坚毅的整合运动术师","text":"是。","id":141,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"等等。","id":143,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"1","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"整合运动也要有人......和她一并奋战到了最后。","id":145,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"2","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"坚毅的整合运动术师","text":"......我明白了。","id":147,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"坚毅的整合运动术师","text":"照顾好我的家人，他们还在城里。","id":148,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"1","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"当然，我向你许诺。","id":150,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":151},{"type":"Character","id":152},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":153},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":154},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":155},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":157},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"......把他的尸体弄得再像回事一些......好，就这样。","id":159,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动士兵","text":"W很快就会察觉到的......我们走。","id":160,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":161},{"type":"Character","id":162},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"Background","id":164},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"啊......","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"没让赫德雷跟来......果然，是正确的......","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......啧。","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"原来，切尔诺伯格街道上的景观树......","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"居然......是桦树......","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"......哈哈。","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"伊内丝","text":"差不多的风景，和那里......都是，交叉的影子......","id":174},{"type":"Dialog","id":175},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":176},{"type":"Image","id":177}],"characters":["赫德雷","伊内丝","整合运动士兵","坚毅的整合运动术师"]}